The paper discusses theory and algorithms for improving AI systems with quantifiable guarantees, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of inner product calculations, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV). The scalability and potential for deployment in embedded environments suggest a focus on data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the use of stochastic separation theorems suggests a focus on neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE).
